Experiment 20: Perform Post-Exploitation Activities Using Meterpreter
Aim
To perform post-exploitation activities using Meterpreter and retrieve system information, running processes,
and network connections.
Introduction
Meterpreter is an advanced Metasploit payload used after successful exploitation for system analysis and
control.
Procedure
Step 1: Open Meterpreter Session
After successful exploitation, Meterpreter session opens automatically.
Step 2: Retrieve System Information
sysinfo
Step 3: View Current User
getuid
Step 4: List Running Processes
ps
Step 5: View Network Connections
netstat
Output
OS information displayed
User information displayed
Processes listed
Network connections displayed
Result
